{\b What is RSVP?}\par
\par
RSVP stands for {\i Rapid Serial Visual Presentation}. It displays text one word at a time, allowing you to read faster without moving your eyes across the page.\par
\par
{\b Key Features:}\par
\par
\bullet  Fast reading speeds up to 900 words per minute\par
\bullet  Automatic progress saving\par
\bullet  Multiple theme options\par
\bullet  Keyboard shortcuts for easy control\par
\par
The {\b Optimal Recognition Point} technique highlights the letter your eye naturally focuses on. This is typically the second or third letter of each word, depending on word length.\par
